<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>The Delta Issue — A Documentary Workshop Publication</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;0,800;0,900;1,400;1,500;1,600;1,700;1,900&family=Source+Serif+4:ital,opsz,wght@0,8..60,400;0,8..60,500;0,8..60,600;1,8..60,400;1,8..60,500&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root{
    --paper:#f6f1e4;
    --paper-white:#fbf8f0;
    --ink:#1a1a18;
    --navy:#1b2a4a;
    --navy-deep:#101b30;
    --red:#a8402f;
    --rule: rgba(26,26,24,0.16);
    --rule-strong: rgba(26,26,24,0.55);
    --charcoal-soft:#4a4438;
    --maxw: 900px;
  }
  *{box-sizing:border-box;}
  body{
    margin:0;
    background:var(--paper);
    color:var(--ink);
    font-family:'Source Serif 4', serif;
    font-size:18px;
    line-height:1.65;
  }
  ::selection{background:var(--navy); color:var(--paper-white);}
  h1,h2,h3,h4{
    font-family:'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-weight:700;
    margin:0;
    line-height:1.06;
  }
  .eyebrow{
    font-family:'Source Serif 4', serif;
    text-transform:uppercase;
    letter-spacing:.12em;
    font-size:13px;
    font-weight:600;
    color:var(--navy);
  }
  .meta{
    font-family:'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size:12px;
    color:var(--charcoal-soft);
  }
  a{color:inherit;}
  img{max-width:100%;display:block;}

  /* ---------- SPINE NAV / TAB BAR ---------- */
  #spine{
    position:fixed; top:0; left:0; bottom:0; width:66px;
    background:var(--navy-deep); z-index:500;
    display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center; padding:18px 0;
    border-right:1px solid rgba(246,241,228,0.1);
  }
  #spine .mark{
    width:30px;height:30px;border:1.5px solid var(--paper); border-radius:50%;
    display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
    font-family:'Playfair Display'; font-weight:700; font-size:12px; color:var(--paper);
    margin-bottom:22px; flex-shrink:0; cursor:pointer;
  }
  #spine-list{list-style:none; margin:0; padding:0; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:2px; overflow-y:auto; flex:1; scrollbar-width:none; width:100%;}
  #spine-list::-webkit-scrollbar{display:none;}
  #spine-list li a{
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; height:38px; width:100%;
    text-decoration:none; cursor:pointer;
    font-family:'Inter'; font-weight:600; font-size:11px; color:rgba(246,241,228,0.45);
    position:relative; transition:color .2s ease;
  }
  #spine-list li a:hover{color:var(--paper);}
  #spine-list li a.active{color:#e0a97e;}
  #spine-list li a.active::before{content:""; position:absolute; left:0; top:6px; bottom:6px; width:3px; background:var(--red);}

  main{margin-left:66px;}
  .wrap{max-width:var(--maxw); margin:0 auto; padding:0 34px;}

  /* ---------- TAB PANEL SYSTEM ---------- */
  .tab-panel{display:none;}
  .tab-panel.active{display:block; animation:fadeIn .3s ease;}
  @keyframes fadeIn{from{opacity:0; transform:translateY(6px);} to{opacity:1; transform:translateY(0);}}

  .tab-pager{
    display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center;
    padding:34px 34px 56px; max-width:var(--maxw); margin:0 auto;
    font-family:'Inter'; font-weight:600; font-size:12.5px; border-top:1px solid var(--rule);
    color:var(--navy);
  }
  .tab-pager a{text-decoration:none; cursor:pointer; display:flex; align-items:center; gap:8px;}
  .tab-pager a:hover{color:var(--red);}
  .tab-pager .p-next{margin-left:auto; text-align:right;}
  .tab-pager small{display:block; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:.08em; font-size:10px; opacity:.65; margin-bottom:3px; font-weight:500;}

  /* running header ribbon, top & bottom of each spread, like the print issue */
  .running-head{
    display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center;
    padding:22px 34px; max-width:var(--maxw); margin:0 auto;
    font-family:'Source Serif 4'; font-weight:600; font-size:12px;
    text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:.1em; color:var(--navy);
    border-bottom:1px solid var(--rule);
  }
  .running-head .rh-crumb{display:flex; align-items:center; gap:8px; color:var(--charcoal-soft); font-weight:500;}
  .running-head .rh-crumb .arrow{color:var(--red); font-size:10px;}
  .running-head.bottom{border-bottom:none; border-top:1px solid var(--rule);}

  /* ---------- COVER (full-bleed photographic wash) ---------- */
  #cover{
    min-height:100vh; color:var(--paper-white);
    background:
      linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(20,16,10,.15) 0%, rgba(20,16,10,.55) 78%, rgba(10,8,5,.75) 100%),
      linear-gradient(200deg, #8a7256 0%, #cbb98a 28%, #e7d8b8 52%, #9aa8ad 78%, #5a6b74 100%);
  }
  #cover .cover-inner{min-height:100vh; display:flex; flex-direction:column; justify-content:space-between; padding:40px 34px 24px;}
  .cover-top{display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:flex-start; font-family:'Inter'; font-weight:600; font-size:12px; letter-spacing:.08em; text-transform:uppercase; color:rgba(251,248,240,0.8);}
  .cover-mid{margin:auto 0; padding:64px 0 24px;}
  .cover-mid .eyebrow{color:#f0d9b5; margin-bottom:16px; display:block;}
  .cover-title{font-family:'Playfair Display'; font-size:clamp(48px, 9.5vw, 108px); font-weight:400; letter-spacing:-0.01em; color:var(--paper-white);}
  .cover-title .hl-italic{font-style:italic; font-weight:400;}
  .cover-title .hl-bold{font-weight:800;}
  .cover-dek{font-family:'Source Serif 4'; font-style:italic; font-size:19px; max-width:520px; margin-top:22px; color:rgba(251,248,240,0.88);}
  .cover-bottom{display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:flex-end; font-family:'Inter'; font-weight:500; font-size:12px; color:rgba(251,248,240,0.7);}

  /* photo / interview placeholders */
  .photo-slot{
    border:1.5px dashed rgba(26,26,24,0.35); background:rgba(26,26,24,0.025);
    padding:22px; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:8px; justify-content:center;
    aspect-ratio: var(--ar, 16/10); position:relative;
  }
  .photo-slot .ph-label{font-family:'Inter'; font-weight:600; font-size:11.5px; letter-spacing:.03em; color:var(--navy); text-transform:uppercase;}
  .photo-slot .ph-suggest{font-family:'Inter'; font-size:12.5px; color:var(--red); line-height:1.55;}
  .pictured{font-family:'Source Serif 4'; font-style:italic; font-size:14.5px; color:var(--charcoal-soft); margin-top:8px;}
  .pictured b{font-style:normal; font-weight:600; color:var(--ink);}

  /* ---------- GENERIC SECTION ---------- */
  .section-front{background:var(--paper); padding:56px 0 20px;}
  .front-head{margin-bottom:30px;}
  .front-head .eyebrow{margin-bottom:8px; display:block;}
  .front-head h2{font-size:clamp(32px,5vw,48px); font-weight:700;}

  /* mixed-weight headline helper spans */
  .hl-italic{font-style:italic; font-weight:400;}
  .hl-bold{font-weight:800;}
  .hl-navy{color:var(--navy);}

  /* ---------- CHAPTER OPENERS (light, photographic) ---------- */
  .chapter-open{background:var(--paper); padding:52px 0 8px;}
  .chapter-num{font-family:'Inter'; font-weight:700; font-size:12.5px; letter-spacing:.16em; color:var(--red); margin-bottom:14px; text-transform:uppercase;}
  .chapter-open h2{font-size:clamp(36px,6vw,64px); color:var(--navy); max-width:820px;}
  .chapter-dek{font-family:'Source Serif 4'; font-style:italic; font-size:19px; color:var(--charcoal-soft); max-width:600px; margin-top:16px;}
  .chapter-open .photo-slot{margin-top:32px; --ar:21/9;}

  .chapter-body{background:var(--paper); padding:40px 0 0;}
  .lede{font-size:21px; color:var(--ink); max-width:680px;}
  .lede + p, p.body-p{margin-top:20px; max-width:680px; color:var(--charcoal-soft); font-size:17.5px;}
  .grid2{display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:28px; margin:32px 0;}
  .grid3{display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr); gap:20px; margin:32px 0;}

  /* small italic pull quote (inline, magazine-style) */
  blockquote.pull{
    margin:36px 0; max-width:680px;
    font-family:'Playfair Display'; font-size:27px; line-height:1.28; color:var(--navy);
  }
  blockquote.pull .hl-italic{font-style:italic; font-weight:500;}
  blockquote.pull .hl-bold{font-weight:800; font-style:normal;}
  blockquote.pull cite{display:block; font-family:'Inter'; font-style:normal; font-weight:600; font-size:11.5px; letter-spacing:.05em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--charcoal-soft); margin-top:14px;}

  /* big statement-style claim, like "ONLY GENERATIONAL POVERTY" */
  .claim{
    font-family:'Playfair Display'; font-weight:800; text-transform:uppercase;
    font-size:clamp(28px,4.6vw,46px); line-height:1.05; color:var(--ink); margin:40px 0 8px; max-width:760px;
  }
  .claim .hl-italic{font-style:italic; font-weight:500; text-transform:none;}

  /* interview quote-slot for named participants */
  .voice-slot{border-top:1px solid var(--rule); padding-top:16px; margin-top:24px;}
  .voice-slot .who{font-family:'Inter'; font-weight:700; font-size:12px; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:.05em; color:var(--red); margin-bottom:6px;}
  .voice-slot .prompt{font-family:'Source Serif 4'; font-style:italic; color:var(--charcoal-soft); font-size:16.5px;}

  /* ---------- BAR CHART (poverty-by-county style) ---------- */
  .bar-chart{margin:32px 0; max-width:680px;}
  .bar-row{display:grid; grid-template-columns:110px 1fr 46px; align-items:center; gap:12px; margin-bottom:7px;}
  .bar-row .b-label{font-family:'Inter'; font-size:12px; color:var(--ink); text-align:right;}
  .bar-track{background:rgba(26,26,24,0.08); height:14px; position:relative;}
  .bar-fill{background:var(--navy); height:100%;}
  .bar-row .b-val{font-family:'Inter'; font-weight:600; font-size:11.5px; color:var(--charcoal-soft);}
  .bar-source{font-family:'Inter'; font-size:11px; color:var(--charcoal-soft); margin-top:6px;}

  /* simple stat row (single figures) */
  .stat-row{display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:36px; margin:32px 0;}
  .stat{max-width:190px;}
  .stat .s-num{font-family:'Playfair Display'; font-weight:800; font-size:40px; color:var(--navy); line-height:1;}
  .stat .s-label{font-family:'Inter'; font-size:12px; color:var(--charcoal-soft); margin-top:6px; line-height:1.5;}
  .stat .s-source{font-family:'Inter'; font-size:10px; color:var(--charcoal-soft); opacity:.7; margin-top:6px;}

  /* ---------- FRAMED SPREAD (hairline border, for archival pages) ---------- */
  .framed{border:1px solid var(--rule-strong); margin:36px 0; padding:36px;}
  .framed-title{font-family:'Playfair Display'; font-weight:800; color:var(--navy); font-size:clamp(24px,3.6vw,34px); margin-bottom:8px;}
  .framed-sub{font-family:'Source Serif 4'; font-style:italic; color:var(--charcoal-soft); font-size:15px; margin-bottom:26px; max-width:560px;}

  /* newspaper-clipping collage placeholders */
  .clipping-field{position:relative; min-height:420px; margin:8px 0;}
  .clipping{
    position:absolute; background:var(--paper-white); border:1px solid var(--rule-strong);
    box-shadow:0 8px 18px rgba(26,26,24,0.14); padding:14px; font-family:'Inter';
  }
  .clipping .c-mast{font-family:'Playfair Display'; font-weight:700; font-size:13px; border-bottom:1px solid var(--ink); padding-bottom:4px; margin-bottom:6px;}
  .clipping .c-head{font-family:'Inter'; font-weight:700; font-size:11px; line-height:1.4; text-transform:uppercase;}
  .clipping .c-label{font-size:9px; color:var(--charcoal-soft); margin-top:8px;}

  /* photographed historical marker placeholder (Blues Trail / Freedom Trail style) */
  .marker-row{display:flex; gap:22px; flex-wrap:wrap; margin:34px 0;}
  .marker-photo{
    width:190px; background:linear-gradient(160deg,#101b30,#22314e);
    border-radius:8px 8px 46px 46px; padding:20px 16px 16px; position:relative;
    box-shadow:0 14px 26px rgba(16,27,48,0.35); transform:rotate(var(--rot,-1.5deg));
    border:2px solid rgba(224,169,126,0.25);
  }
  .marker-photo::before{content:""; position:absolute; top:8px; left:50%; transform:translateX(-50%); width:16px; height:16px; border:1px solid #e0a97e; border-radius:50%; opacity:.55;}
  .marker-photo .mk-eyebrow{font-family:'Inter'; font-size:9px; letter-spacing:.1em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#e0a97e; margin-top:20px; text-align:center;}
  .marker-photo .mk-title{font-family:'Playfair Display'; font-weight:800; font-size:16px; color:var(--paper-white); text-align:center; margin-top:6px; line-height:1.15;}
  .marker-photo .mk-sub{font-family:'Inter'; font-size:9.5px; color:rgba(251,248,240,0.65); text-align:center; margin-top:8px; line-height:1.4;}

  /* portrait grid, "Faces of..." style */
  .portrait-grid{display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr); gap:18px; margin:32px 0;}
  .portrait{text-align:center;}
  .portrait .photo-slot{--ar:1/1; border-radius:50%;}
  .portrait .p-name{font-family:'Playfair Display'; font-weight:700; font-size:14px; margin-top:10px; color:var(--navy);}
  .portrait .p-role{font-family:'Inter'; font-size:11px; color:var(--charcoal-soft);}

  /* ---------- TOC (stacked wordmark) ---------- */
  #toc-front{background:var(--paper);}
  .toc-wordmark{
    font-family:'Playfair Display'; font-weight:800; text-transform:uppercase;
    font-size:clamp(64px,13vw,168px); line-height:0.82; color:var(--navy);
    letter-spacing:-0.01em; opacity:.94; margin-bottom:10px;
  }
  .toc-layout{display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1.3fr; gap:40px; margin-top:20px;}
  .toc-quotes{display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:30px; padding-top:8px;}
  .toc-quotes .tq{font-family:'Playfair Display'; font-style:italic; font-weight:500; font-size:19px; color:var(--charcoal-soft); line-height:1.35;}
  .toc-list-item{border-bottom:1px solid var(--rule); padding:14px 0; cursor:pointer; display:flex; gap:16px;}
  .toc-list-item:hover .tl-title{color:var(--red);}
  .toc-list-item .tl-pg{font-family:'Inter'; font-weight:700; font-size:12px; color:var(--charcoal-soft); width:44px; flex-shrink:0; padding-top:3px;}
  .toc-list-item .tl-title{font-family:'Playfair Display'; font-weight:700; font-size:19px; color:var(--ink); transition:color .15s;}
  .toc-list-item .tl-desc{font-family:'Source Serif 4'; font-style:italic; font-size:14px; color:var(--charcoal-soft); margin-top:3px;}

  /* ---------- FOOTER / CLOSING ---------- */
  #closing{background:var(--paper);}
  .team-grid{display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr); gap:16px; margin-top:24px;}
  .team-card{border-top:2px solid var(--navy); padding:14px 4px 0; font-family:'Inter'; font-size:12px; color:var(--charcoal-soft);}
  .team-card .name{font-family:'Playfair Display'; font-weight:700; font-size:16px; color:var(--navy); margin-bottom:4px;}
  .back-cover{background:var(--navy-deep); color:var(--paper-white); padding:80px 0; text-align:center; margin-top:20px;}
  .back-cover h3{font-family:'Playfair Display'; font-size:clamp(26px,4vw,36px); max-width:640px; margin:0 auto 22px; font-weight:700;}
  .praise{font-family:'Playfair Display'; font-style:italic; font-size:19px; max-width:560px; margin:0 auto 14px; color:rgba(251,248,240,0.9); font-weight:500;}
  .praise cite{display:block; font-family:'Inter'; font-style:normal; font-weight:600; font-size:11px; margin-top:8px; color:#e0a97e; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:.05em;}
  footer.credits{background:var(--navy-deep); color:rgba(251,248,240,0.45); font-family:'Inter'; font-size:11px; padding:22px 0 36px; text-align:center;}

  #builder-note{
    background:var(--navy); color:var(--paper-white); font-family:'Inter'; font-weight:500; font-size:12.5px;
    padding:10px 16px 10px 82px; line-height:1.5; position:relative; z-index:400;
  }
  #builder-note b{text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:.05em;}
  #builder-note button{background:var(--red); color:var(--paper-white); border:none; font-family:'Inter'; font-weight:600; font-size:11px; padding:4px 10px; cursor:pointer; margin-left:10px; border-radius:3px;}

  @media (max-width:760px){
    #spine{top:auto; bottom:0; left:0; right:0; height:56px; width:100%; flex-direction:row; padding:0 8px; border-right:none; border-top:1px solid rgba(246,241,228,0.1); z-index:600;}
    #spine .mark{display:none;}
    #spine-list{flex-direction:row; overflow-x:auto; overflow-y:visible; align-items:center; height:100%;}
    #spine-list li a{height:100%; padding:0 12px; white-space:nowrap;}
    #spine-list li a.active::before{left:6px; right:6px; top:auto; bottom:6px; height:2px; width:auto;}
    main{margin-left:0; padding-bottom:56px;}
    .grid2, .grid3{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
    .team-grid, .portrait-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);}
    .toc-layout{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
    .bar-row{grid-template-columns:80px 1fr 40px;}
    #builder-note{padding-left:16px;}
    .running-head{flex-direction:column; align-items:flex-start; gap:4px;}
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div id="builder-note">
  <b>Prototype note —</b> Restyled to match your printed issue: cream stock, navy heads, hairline frames, "Pictured:" captions, and photographed marker/clipping placeholders. Swap dashed boxes for your own images and transcripts before publishing. <button onclick="document.getElementById('builder-note').style.display='none'">Dismiss</button>
</div>

<nav id="spine">
  <div class="mark" onclick="showTab('cover')">DI</div>
  <ul id="spine-list">
    <li><a data-tab="cover">Cvr</a></li>
    <li><a data-tab="intro">In</a></li>
    <li><a data-tab="toc-front">Toc</a></li>
    <li><a data-tab="directors-note">Dn</a></li>
    <li><a data-tab="voices">Vo</a></li>
    <li><a data-tab="ch-mississippi">01</a></li>
    <li><a data-tab="ch-education">02</a></li>
    <li><a data-tab="ch-healthcare">03</a></li>
    <li><a data-tab="ch-immigrants">04</a></li>
    <li><a data-tab="ch-faiths">05</a></li>
    <li><a data-tab="ch-blues">06</a></li>
    <li><a data-tab="ch-civilrights">07</a></li>
    <li><a data-tab="ch-media">08</a></li>
    <li><a data-tab="ch-commemoration">09</a></li>
    <li><a data-tab="closing">Cl</a></li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<main>

  <!-- ============ COVER ============ -->
  <section id="cover" class="tab-panel">
   <div class="cover-inner">
    <div class="cover-top">
      <span>The Delta Issue</span>
      <span>Vol. 04 — Documentary Workshop Publication</span>
    </div>
    <div class="cover-mid wrap" style="padding-left:0;padding-right:0;max-width:100%;">
      <span class="eyebrow">A field report from the Mississippi Delta</span>
      <h1 class="cover-title">Land, <span class="hl-italic">Water,</span><br>and <span class="hl-bold">What Remains</span></h1>
      <p class="cover-dek">Nine chapters of reporting, portraiture, and oral history built with the people of the Delta — on flood and cotton, faith and isolation, the blues and the civil rights road, and who gets to tell the story of a place.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="cover-bottom wrap" style="padding-left:0;padding-right:0;max-width:100%;">
      <span>Est. workshop, est. issue no. 4</span>
      <span>~48 pages</span>
    </div>
   </div>
   <div class="tab-pager"></div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ INTRODUCTION ============ -->
  <section id="intro" class="tab-panel section-front">
    <div class="running-head"><span class="eyebrow" style="margin:0;">Introduction</span><span class="meta">Front Matter · 01</span></div>
    <div class="wrap" style="padding-top:36px;">
      <p class="lede">Poetry and photography, paired, to set the scene before the reporting begins.</p>
      <div class="grid2">
        <div class="photo-slot" style="--ar:4/5;">
          <div class="ph-label">Opening spread — image</div>
          <div class="ph-suggest">A road photo at dusk, big sky and clouds — the tone your own intro spread used. Wide field, levee line, or a lone figure against sky all work.</div>
        </div>
        <div style="padding:12px 0;">
          <h3 style="font-family:'Playfair Display'; font-size:22px; color:var(--navy); margin-bottom:16px;">I, Too</h3>
          <p class="body-p" style="font-style:italic; margin-top:0;">[Reserve this page for an original poem by a workshop participant — 8 to 16 lines. If you'd like to open with "I, Too" by Langston Hughes again, secure reprint permission first, since it's still under copyright; otherwise credit and link to it rather than reprinting the full text.]</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="tab-pager"></div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ TOC ============ -->
  <section id="toc-front" class="tab-panel section-front">
    <div class="wrap" style="padding-top:8px;">
      <div class="toc-wordmark">Contents</div>
      <div class="meta" style="margin-bottom:10px;">Preface &amp; Table of Contents</div>
      <div class="toc-layout">
        <div class="toc-quotes">
          <p class="tq">"The Delta is more diverse, culturally rich, beautiful, impoverished, rural, vibrant, and complicated than I had imagined."</p>
          <p class="tq">"This is my home, too."</p>
          <p class="tq">"Heaven and earth so close, but still miles apart."</p>
